messages.content: What additional image formats does the Extended Save Image custom node support?
The Extended Save Image custom node supports saving images in JPEG and WEBP formats.
Does the Extended Save Image custom node support lossless and lossy compression for WEBP images?
Yes, it supports both lossless and lossy compression for WEBP images.
How can I install the Extended Save Image custom node?
Clone the repository into the `ComfyUI/custom_nodes` folder with `git clone https://github.com/palant/extended-saveimage-comfyui` and restart ComfyUI.
Can the resulting images from the Extended Save Image custom node be used to load a workflow?
Yes, the resulting images from the Extended Save Image custom node can be used to load a workflow.
Does the Extended Save Image custom node embed metadata in the images?
Yes, metadata is embedded in the images as usual.
